## 5. Historical Calculation Engines (Legacy Modules)

While [ESCAL212](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL212) represents the modern baseline of the calculation pricing rules, the source codebase includes 20 specific legacy legacy execution modules ([ESCAL056](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL056) through [ESCAL202](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL202)) intended to price retrospective claims precisely based on the static data applicable during those years.

### Rule HIST-001: Historical Versioning & Routing
The controller ([ESDRV212](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESDRV212)) selects the appropriate execution engine by directly mapping the Calendar Year of the Bill Date to a particular static module. The executed rules remain structurally identical to the logic documented for [ESCAL212](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL212), except they substitute historically locked hardcoded values for variables such as Base Rates, low-volume thresholds, or distinct Age Multipliers mapping to those specific years. 
*   **<= 2005**: Calls [ESCAL056](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL056)
*   **2006 -> 2009**: Calls [ESCAL062](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL062), [070](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL070), [071](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL071)(patch), [080](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL080), [091](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL091) respectively.
*   **2010 -> 2013**: Calls [ESCAL100](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL100), [117](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL117), [122](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL122), [130](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL130) respectively. 
*   **2014 -> 2018**: Calls [ESCAL140](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL140), [151](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL151), [160](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL160), [170](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL170), [171](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL171)(patch), [180](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL180) respectively.
*   **2019 -> 2021**: Calls [ESCAL191](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL191), [200](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL200), [202](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL202)(patch) and [212](file:///Users/rohitkelapure/Downloads/ESRDCY212MainframePricerReleaseFiles/ESCAL212) respectively.
